description: KYIV, Ukraine (AP) — Russian forces resumed scattered attacks on Kyiv, western Ukraine and beyond Saturday in an explosive reminder to Ukrainians and their Western supporters that  the whole country  remains under threat despite Russia’s pivot toward mounting a new offensive in the east.
